        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 1. Different stages of development of the studied species. Mating of Plagiometriona emarcida and Plagiometriona forcipata in the field (A), eggs (B), a P. emarcida female ovipositing with a phoretic eulophid wasp circled (B), larva (D), pupa (E), and a P. emarcida teneral adult. Scale 2 mm." ;
